reviewText: I got this because of Roy Atwell and he is not in it,I was very disappointed.
I loved People are Funny in the 1950s when I was a teenager, but find the humor dated and not particularly funny in the 21st century.

This is a simple and cute film that shows the natural acting of Ozzie Nelson  ( of The Adventures of Ozzie & Harriet TV show).
I bought this for Joe DeRita bit part. He was a natural for the 3 Stoogies. If you are a fan of both Ozzie & Joe then enjoy this mild bit of fluff.
It;s great to see the show again after all the years. The movie isn't  much good but episode is great. With they brought out more of the Episodes on DVDi'll would buy'em
